<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.6">
<l>nīyu nāṉumin nērniṟkiṉ mēṉmaṟṟōr</l>
<l>nōyuñ cārkkoṭā ṉeñcamē coṉṉēṉ</l>
<l>ṟāyun tantaiyu māyiv vulakiṉil</l>
<l>vāyu mīcaṉ maṇivaṇṇa ṉentaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“If you and I stand before [him] henceforth he will not give room</l>
<l>to all the pains of others , o heart” I said.</l>
<l>Being mother and father in this world</l>
<l>the lord prevails, the saphire-coloured one, our father.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
